import { createApp } from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import vuetify from './plugins/vuetify'
import { loadFonts } from './plugins/webfontloader'
import Uppy from '@uppy/core'
import Dashboard from '@uppy/dashboard'

loadFonts()

const uppy = new Uppy()
uppy.use(Dashboard, {
  target: 'body',
  inline: true,
})

createApp(App)
  .use(vuetify)
  .mount('#app')
